<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/contact.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header class="header">
        <nav class="nav-bar">
            <%- include('partials/logo') %>
            <ul>
                <li><a id="open-offcanvas" href="/signin" class="button">Sign In</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <section id="cta-contact">
        <div class="text">
            <h1>We're Here to Help!</h1>
            <p>If you have any questions, comments, or just want to get in touch with us, feel free to use the form
                below. Our team is ready to assist you and answer all your concerns. Your feedback is very important to
                us, so we look forward to hearing from you soon!</p>
            <a href="#" class="button" id="contact-us">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <main>
        <div class="main">
            <section id="faq">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="faq-items">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="question">
                            <h3>What is Movie Collector?</h3>
                            <img src="images/icons/add.png" alt="add/remove">
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer">
                            <p>Movie Collector is an app designed to help users organize and manage their personal movie
                                collections. You can easily add, categorize, and track the movies you own, want to
                                watch, or
                                have
                                already seen.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="question">
                            <h3>How do I add a movie to my collection?</h3>
                            <img src="images/icons/add.png" alt="add/remove">
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer">
                            <p>To add a movie, simply search for the title using the search bar, then click "Add to
                                Collection."
                                You
                                can also manually input movie details if it’s not found in our database.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="question">
                            <h3>Can I track movies I want to watch?</h3>
                            <img src="images/icons/add.png" alt="add/remove">
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer">
                            <p>Yes! You can create a "Watchlist" to track movies you want to watch in the future. Just
                                add
                                them
                                to
                                your watchlist from the movie’s detail page.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="question">
                            <h3>Can I export my movie collection?</h3>
                            <img src="images/icons/add.png" alt="add/remove">
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer">
                            <p>Yes, you can export your entire movie collection to a CSV file for backup or use in other
                                applications. Go to "Settings" and select the "Export Collection" option.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="question">
                            <h3>Is Movie Collector free?</h3>
                            <img src="images/icons/add.png" alt="add/remove">
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer">
                            <p>Movie Collector offers a free version with basic features, and a premium version with
                                additional
                                features such as unlimited collection size, advanced sorting, and cloud backup.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="question">
                            <h3>How do I contact support?</h3>
                            <img src="images/icons/add.png" alt="add/remove">
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer">
                            <p>If you need help, you can contact our support team via the "Help & Support" section in
                                the
                                app,
                                or
                                send an email to support@moviecollectorapp.com.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section id="contact-info">
                <h2>Contact Information</h2>
                <div class="contact-details">
                    <!-- Email -->
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <img src="images/icons/email.png" alt="Email Icon" class="contact-icon">
                        <div>
                            <h3>Email Us</h3>
                            <p><a href="mailto:support@moviecollectorapp.com">support@moviecollectorapp.com</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="separate"></div>
                    <!-- Phone -->
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <img src="images/icons/phone-call.png" alt="Phone Icon" class="contact-icon">
                        <div>
                            <h3>Call Us</h3>
                            <p><a href="tel:+954567321">+954567321</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="separate"></div>
                    <!-- Social Media -->
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <img src="images/icons/social-media.png" alt="Social Media Icon" class="contact-icon">
                        <div>
                            <h3>Follow Us</h3>
                            <div class="social-media">
                                <img src="images/social_media/facebook.png" alt="">
                                <img src="images/social_media/linkedin.png" alt="">
                                <img src="images/social_media/instagram.png" alt="">
                                <img src="images/social_media/twitter.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </footer>
    <%- include('partials/fab') %>
    <script src="javascripts/dialog.js"></script>
    <script src="javascripts/faq.js"></script>
</body>
</html>